And-.. some new voices from #22, FM random mode.

For those that don't know, "my guys" claim to see their "Princess Kiera", 
instead of this middle aged bald man. They seemed to imply in one of the 
older voices that this "Princess" was once the "Queen of Atlantis". There's 
also been references to a similar life time in Ancient Egypt, as well as one 
not on Earth. Who knows.....?

I'm often reluctant to share these gender bending voices because of 
perceived societal biases, but I can't see wtihholding either--it what I 
get.

Frank-S
